    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is due to an update in vue router likely that breaks the `event.state` in the popstate handler causing the state to be empty. the solution is to always read:\n\n```\n          onUpdate(cb) {\n            this._onPopState = () => {\n              cb(this.read());\n            };\n            window.addEventListener('popstate', this._onPopState);\n          },\n```\n\nhttps://codesandbox.io/p/devbox/quizzical-david-8pndk9?file=%2Fsrc%2Fviews%2FHome.vue%3A71%2C31&workspaceId=ws_Fs32YmkEDgsiKNjerGYqmX\n\nI'll update the demo to be this as well",
